---

## Project Name

Quiz Platform with Leaderboard

---

## Project Description

A fully interactive quiz application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

The application allows users to answer multiple-choice questions, track their score, and view a leaderboard of top performers. It includes a timer system, progress tracking, and visual feedback for correct and wrong answers.

All scores are stored using Local Storage, making the data persistent across sessions.

---

## Features

- Multiple-choice quiz system
- Real-time scoring system
- Timer for each question
- Progress bar indicator
- Correct and wrong answer highlighting
- Leaderboard system with ranking
- Data stored using Local Storage
- Responsive and modern UI design

---

## Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)

---

## Project Functionality

- Users answer quiz questions one by one
- Timer automatically moves to next question
- Score updates based on correct answers
- Progress bar shows completion status
- Final score is displayed at the end
- Leaderboard stores and displays top scores
- Data persists even after page refresh

